{"tid":343444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機管局推三跑曾研究：去北京坐高鐵比飛機「無競爭力」","createTime":"2017-08-01T12:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T05:21:07.000Z","uid":51271,"like":60,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"003c0a52b9f3ac2fa92b9595835cd1939f9d965e","tid":343444,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170801/s00001/27946bfccb1558ae2c24a8c4dbc1d126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170801%2Fs00001%2F27946bfccb1558ae2c24a8c4dbc1d126.jpg&h=575034b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170801/s00001/1501587116610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170801%2Fs00001%2F1501587116610&d=g6HUuDliaoTZmEauGmvtRJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b6656968\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170801%2Fs00001%2F1501587116610&h=987ae4a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170801/s00001/1501587116610</a><br />\n<br />\n政府近期落力Hard Sell高鐵一地兩檢嘅好處，之前喺政府新聞處facebook上載圖片，話坐高鐵由香港返廣州，喺唔停中途站下車程只需48分鐘，但坐飛機就要60分鐘，而且仲需要提早1至2個鐘到機場，單比行程都已經快12分鐘，但就畀唔少網民批評係誇大失實。不過，原來機管局喺2011年力推目前造價高達1415億元嘅第三條跑道項目時，就曾經引用顧問研究，證明坐飛機去內地大部分城市都比高鐵快，當中更直指話如果到北京、重慶、成都呢啲大城市，高鐵對比飛機完全「無競爭力」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府喺上星期二公布高鐵一地兩檢方案之後，近日係咁打民意戰，力銷高鐵嘅交通同經濟效益，當中政府新聞處facebook最近上載4幅圖片，話坐高鐵既環保又快捷，仲話如果由本港到廣州嘅話，高鐵唔停中途站下只需48分鐘。港鐵主席馬時亨日前亦都話，如果高鐵有一地兩檢，佢去北京嘅話「一定會乘搭高鐵，不會乘搭飛機。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，運房局舊年5月回覆傳媒時，就話過高鐵啟用初期每日會有114對列車，當中只有11對係由西九龍站直達到廣州南站，比例不足一成。<br />\n<br />\n而新民主同盟區議員譚凱邦今日就搵番2011年機管局力推第三跑工程上馬時嘅諮詢文件，當時機管局引用顧問公司同運房局嘅數據，比較咗香港前往16個內地城市嘅車程，當中證實咗10個城市係坐飛機比高鐵快，文件仲列明其中5個城市，包括北京、重慶、成都、西安同昆明，對比飛機「高鐵無競爭力」。至於坐高鐵快過飛機嘅城市就包括汕頭、長沙、南京、廈門等。<br />\n<br />\n譚凱邦就批評政府卑鄙，「機管局推銷三跑時，就話長途高鐵冇競爭力；而林鄭7月9日參觀石崗高鐵停泊處時，就話搭高鐵去上海、北京好方便，咁邊個先啱？」佢批評政府「推銷三跑時就容許機管局踩低高鐵，宜家推銷高鐵時就講到上海、北京好似係香港隔離咁」。"},{"pid":"e9281575dea7576bb648e8fc5f6aae5a0908e4a3","tid":343444,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:46:00.000Z","msg":"大部份人唔會坐4個鐘以上既高鐵,但香港4個鐘內高鐵去到既城市有幾多?"},{"pid":"b3fc511100cde140bf9809b00a3b7ab64c13b263","tid":343444,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"昨日的自己成功打倒今日的自己"},{"pid":"319b5fa2862d1d02166c0eb492c675b3dc5dc15b","tid":343444,"uid":11001,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/5/5f/13fs6p.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140313032610\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F5%2F5f%2F13fs6p.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140313032610&h=15d1cdf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a8934c41a358e2ea88f68d58de374d2d6409157","tid":343444,"uid":108133,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"我宜家先知原來咁近都有機去廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf80ecf1834da79efe67d2830d0cc43b9a720355","tid":343444,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:50:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>昨日的自己成功打倒今日的自己</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nR三跑撥款咪講飛機勁囉<br />\n<br />\n講高鐵咪吹火車囉"},{"pid":"2b2af67b1a2d71e8b77ac15a4a6c0dc453297c6b","tid":343444,"uid":48442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:54:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7526a9c4390db425dca4de90b4c73840545cda8d","tid":343444,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛機跟本冇得輸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/005555_386fc335442af7530e09f09ee37b04d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F005555_386fc335442af7530e09f09ee37b04d2.jpg&h=ce3116a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/005556_cb5b33c55fda9ec13002d1ce02bfdff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F005556_cb5b33c55fda9ec13002d1ce02bfdff0.jpg&h=70bfb4da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/02/005557_48bc54a300257fd9bf1fff021306fb28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F02%2F005557_48bc54a300257fd9bf1fff021306fb28.jpg&h=875250dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0344db912d8a929f8562010be3bb09860424db2c","tid":343444,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宜家先知原來咁近都有機去廣州<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c8b0660f3ffb7e4d3cfded703769071b34a017","tid":343444,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:58:30.000Z","msg":"去廣州南站快有撚用咩<br />\n入返廣州市區都要一個鐘<br />\n衰過直通車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b1e347079fc9a4eb2bc6dfe7b174d137eb7c71","tid":343444,"uid":2290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"當中只有11對係由西九龍站直達到<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州南站</span><br />\n你去撚埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa6475d880d4675c955aa823f621c5fab7ae7bd","tid":343444,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當中只有11對係由西九龍站直達到<span style=\"color: red;\">廣州南站</span><br />\n你去撚埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n南站近佛山 番禺<br />\n去天河東站要一個鐘車程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a36e2df47ac95e4e5ae61c37bcece1e2e586c5f","tid":343444,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"超過1000公里距離<br />\n飛機完全無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f451a7d989624686762c2a26384d66f2df2a22f0","tid":343444,"uid":23848,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:54:20.000Z","msg":"咁睇坐高鐵都幾好<br />\n唔慢太多 又有風景睇"},{"pid":"fde9a95c1a1dde8fbc10886d7a76a5613fc4b84b","tid":343444,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de001cc5312108de92a1e94ad7d4baa1525a4e61","tid":343444,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972a2879fae5a1ef40f327806bbebccbc6f7b4d9","tid":343444,"uid":125258,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:07:33.000Z","msg":"用飛行時間比冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你入機場再check 埋in，到上機take off<br />\n呢到都至少個半鐘，仲未計大陸機場濕尻air traffic control經常delay<br />\n<br />\n高鐵預早半個鐘到就得，始終市區入面，再加高鐵一過完customs就可以上車準時走人<br />\n<br />\n不過去遠既地方（北京，上海）都係搭飛機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91920966511c7e8066efab00ca0d1baf36b9dbc","tid":343444,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用飛行時間比冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你入機場再check 埋in，到上機take off<br />\n呢到都至少個半鐘，仲未計大陸機場濕尻air traffic control經常delay<br />\n<br />\n高鐵預早半個鐘到就得，始終市區入面，再加高鐵一過完customs就可以上車準時走人<br />\n<br />\n不過去遠既地方（北京，上海）都係搭飛機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYou don't say... <br />\nChiNa高鐵嗰door-to-door time輸硬"},{"pid":"7f493be7173e9c31686f76a57759596aecc11dd0","tid":343444,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:09:36.000Z","msg":"AAHK vs MTRCL <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81420b8d169a63f81890af22bfa50b5aaff17fb3","tid":343444,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用飛行時間比冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你入機場再check 埋in，到上機take off<br />\n呢到都至少個半鐘，仲未計大陸機場濕尻air traffic control經常delay<br />\n<br />\n高鐵預早半個鐘到就得，始終市區入面，再加高鐵一過完customs就可以上車準時走人<br />\n<br />\n不過去遠既地方（北京，上海）都係搭飛機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中華盲俠，睇多次幅圖"},{"pid":"837b10841eb60fd63fb163e31e353b07c7f78fa6","tid":343444,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:16:29.000Z","msg":"南京遠過上海架喎. ON9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198e1e674da563e47d76676d9fcb55e3db953b8d","tid":343444,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:18:21.000Z","msg":"就公事出差 我唔會只係睇航程時間 特別係上海／北京<br />\n<br />\n1. 大陸機場成日空管 - 經常delay<br />\n2\b. 機場去酒店交通情況 - 成日塞到仆街<br />\n3. 如果火車overnight第2日朝早到 會幾方便有足夠休息 飛機航班時間做但唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以真係睇情況"},{"pid":"2533aed8acd539d70229a087316183c431d711b3","tid":343444,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用飛行時間比冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你入機場再check 埋in，到上機take off<br />\n呢到都至少個半鐘，仲未計大陸機場濕尻air traffic control經常delay<br />\n<br />\n高鐵預早半個鐘到就得，始終市區入面，再加高鐵一過完customs就可以上車準時走人<br />\n<br />\n不過去遠既地方（北京，上海）都係搭飛機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知唔知高鐵成日都停駛架? <br />\n落雨又停駛, 打風又停駛. 落雪又停駛.<br />\n廈深鐵路岩岩起好個時, 我去到汕頭, 就話停駛, 根住趕晒全部人落車, 然後廣播話停駛, 等咗2個鐘都冇消息, 最後要我坐巴士汕頭上廈門."},{"pid":"1fdcca7389747fd80eff6c882d02c1c4a4962449","tid":343444,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用飛行時間比冇意思<br />\n<br />\n你入機場再check 埋in，到上機take off<br />\n呢到都至少個半鐘，仲未計大陸機場濕尻air traffic control經常delay<br />\n<br />\n高鐵預早半個鐘到就得，始終市區入面，再加高鐵一過完customs就可以上車準時走人<br />\n<br />\n不過去遠既地方（北京，上海）都係搭飛機算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中華盲俠，睇多次幅圖</blockquote>佢可能睇漏預計左過關等時間 但佢講既係事不過上面幅圖既預計時間一定唔可靠 坐開就知一delay係好撚delay"},{"pid":"17d341e660a9af99b8c5b1c37698b57ca780ebfe","tid":343444,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就公事出差 我唔會只係睇航程時間 特別係上海／北京<br />\n<br />\n1. 大陸機場成日空管 - 經常delay<br />\n2\b. 機場去酒店交通情況 - 成日塞到仆街<br />\n3. 如果火車overnight第2日朝早到 會幾方便有足夠休息 飛機航班時間做但唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以真係睇情況</blockquote><br />\n中國航空。夠膽死delay你四十個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088dd5097b460868c88ff0f784f2eac3c2868fad","tid":343444,"uid":3673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:25:08.000Z","msg":"試過一次答高鐵去福州， 要5個幾鍾 <br />\n我情願答飛機 機程個半鍾同d 蝗一齊<br />\n好個接近6個鍾同d 蝗係架車到<br />\n有時中途站又成日有人落車，又有d 一家大細唔知做乜鳩得個細佬買左1等座，佢d 老豆老母就買企位 ,企係你格離係咁同個細佬講野，煩撚到好似想你讓個位比佢咁"},{"pid":"c4b4ac4c5b20d3c4a9c9e27900c70a5735d4bec8","tid":343444,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:27:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>就公事出差 我唔會只係睇航程時間 特別係上海／北京<br />\n<br />\n1. 大陸機場成日空管 - 經常delay<br />\n2\b. 機場去酒店交通情況 - 成日塞到仆街<br />\n3. 如果火車overnight第2日朝早到 會幾方便有足夠休息 飛機航班時間做但唔到<br />\n<br />\n所以真係睇情況</blockquote><br />\n中國航空。夠膽死delay你四十個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/n